      <title>铁腕统治者谢赫·哈西娜的迅速倒台标志着孟加拉国进入新时代</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/sheikh-hasina-resignation-marks-new-era-for-bangladesh-after-protests</link>
