    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国总统誓言“尽快”举行选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/bangladesh-president-vows-to-hold-election-as-soon-as-possible</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国长期领导人谢赫·哈西娜于周一在致命抗议活动后下台，该国名义总统承诺“尽快”举行选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/bangladesh-president-vows-to-hold-election-as-soon-as-possible</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 00:56:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国决策者呼吁保持冷静应对全球市场崩盘</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/south-korean-policymakers-urge-calm-against-global-market-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国决策者呼吁公众保持冷静，避免全球股市暴跌。韩国顶级企业股价暴跌，旨在恢复人们对依靠出口拉动而继续增长的经济的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/south-korean-policymakers-urge-calm-against-global-market-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 00:23:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国推出20条措施鼓励人们消费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/the-20-measures-china-s-unveiled-to-get-people-to-spend-their-cash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国已宣布一项20步行动计划以鼓励人们增加消费，但在刺激国内需求方面提供的财政激励措施却很少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/the-20-measures-china-s-unveiled-to-get-people-to-spend-their-cash</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 00:21:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国及其盟友竭力避免可能发生的中东战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/some-impatient-israelis-want-to-preempt-iran-s-promised-reprisal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国及其盟友努力阻止伊朗对以色列的袭击，并避免爆发更大范围的地区战争，因为人们越来越担心，伊朗可能随时对以色列发动袭击，以报复哈马斯高级领导人在德黑兰被杀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/some-impatient-israelis-want-to-preempt-iran-s-promised-reprisal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 17:12:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行因市场崩盘后加息时机遭批评</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/boj-under-fire-for-rate-hike-timing-after-japan-market-meltdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行上周收紧货币政策引发了一波批评，因为这导致日本股市历史性暴跌，并加剧了全球市场动荡 —— 很可能使任何进一步加息的计划被搁置。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/boj-under-fire-for-rate-hike-timing-after-japan-market-meltdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 13:37:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
